{"tid":702405,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【反擊空軍】特步反駁沽空報告 指控不實及誤導","createTime":"2018-06-15T01:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T01:12:33.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2173cf5fd45ebf2e72e50da030ba02f08a4a4421","tid":702405,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529023137_ce20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529023137_ce20.jpg&h=2f7ebcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特步反駁沽空報告 指控不實及誤導<br />\n<br />\n沽空機構GMT Research日前指控多間內地體育品牌，指其是騙子，特步（1368）發公告澄清，反駁沽空報告指控不實及誤導。<br />\n<br />\n特步表示，集團嚴格遵守適用法律及法規經營其業務，概無觸犯會計欺詐。同時一直向外界準確披露其業務營運及財務業績。特步保留向GMT尋求損害或其他賠償而採取法律行動的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180615&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58320211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180615%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58320211&d=bNbl%2FLWCCKDu5uVJf5jIbcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=41784df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180615%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58320211&h=31e97e49\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180615&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58320211</a>"},{"pid":"efcc33a8808b6882cb092c6115dec72770f680f5","tid":702405,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"中國只有__ __才是真的"}]}